Package oogasalad.editor.controller

Class EditorDataAPI

java.lang.Object
oogasalad.editor.controller.EditorDataAPI
public class EditorDataAPI extends Object
Provides an API to manage editor data by interfacing with the various underlying data managers. This class acts as a facade for performing operations on editor objects, layers, groups, and dynamic variables, and delegates tasks to corresponding data managers within an EditorLevelData instance.
Author:
Jacob You
